channel.title: Draynor willow whacker
channel.description: hello im using a draynor willow whacker by darkness but the axe head finder is useless ive lost 3 axe heads within an hour and all axes i can use r steel iron and bronze because of the cost keep buying them when i loose the head, would it be possible for any one to update the axe finder in the script so that it actually works and maybe the ent part please i would be very greatful

item.title: Draynor willow whacker
item.dc:creator: @RSelite RSelite
item.description:
@RSelite wrote:

I made handle for the tree shake it works all the time petty simple all you do is scan a 10 * 10 area of the tree and store those colors in a int array then compare it 's colors every 100 milliseconds with the new colors and for every color that match inc the counter then store new colors in the array and if code it right then the you will see like when tree is shaking you get like 100 20 100 20 100. you see the pattern high then low then high instead of consistent hight value. the hard part is to tell if the the area you scannig is actually part of the tree your chopping.
